OL,3,CCoroner calls for canal safety
OL,4,Cmeasures after student death
OL,6,FA coroner has urged canal bosses to
OL,7,Ftake safety measures after the
OL,8,Faccidental death of a student
OL,9,Ffollowing a night out.
OL,11,FWilliam Webb, 21, from Baxenden, near
OL,12,FAccrington, Lancashire, fell into the
OL,13,FShropshire Union canal in Chester,
OL,14,Fclose to student accommodation in the
OL,15,Fcity.
OL,17,FThe University of Chester student was
OL,18,Freported missing when he failed to
OL,19,Fcome home after he had been drinking
OL,20,Fwith friends in the city on the
OL,21,Fevening of 22 November.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
