OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772572324
OL,3,CCoroner calls for canal safety
OL,4,Cmeasures after student death
OL,6,FAn inquest last month heard that CCTV
OL,7,Ffootage showed Mr Webb walking along a
OL,8,Fpath which runs alongside the canal,
OL,9,Fat about 4.30am on 23 November before
OL,10,F"likely accidentally falling into the
OL,11,Fcanal".
OL,13,FHis body was discovered the following
OL,14,Fday.
OL,16,FArea coroner for Cheshire, Victoria
OL,17,FDavies, said her investigation had
OL,18,Ffound matters of concern as she issued
OL,19,Fa prevention of future deaths report
OL,20,Fto the Canal & River Trust.
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772572324
OL,3,CCoroner calls for canal safety
OL,4,Cmeasures after student death
OL,6,FShe highlighted there was no safety
OL,7,Fequipment which could assist someone
OL,8,Fin the water, and that the distance
OL,9,Fbetween the water level and the ground
OL,10,Fedge would make it difficult to get
OL,11,Fout unaided.
OL,13,FMs Davies said there was also no
OL,14,Fsignage nearby to alert people to the
OL,15,Fpotential risks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
