CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772572324
OL,3,CCoroner calls for canal safety
OL,4,Cmeasures after student death
OL,6,FShe added: "Whilst this is a
OL,7,Fgeneralisation and is by no means all
OL,8,Fstudents, students as a group are
OL,9,Fwithin the demographic of people who
OL,10,Fwill attend the bars, pubs and
OL,11,Fnightclubs of Chester and become
OL,12,Finebriated to varying degrees.
OL,14,F"Once under the influence of alcohol,
OL,15,For perhaps another substance, it is
OL,16,Fthen not inconceivable that they then
OL,17,Ftake less care/are more willing to
OL,18,Fengage in risky behaviours.
OL,26,@nD@LOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
