OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772572324
OL,3,CCoroner calls for canal safety
OL,4,Cmeasures after student death
OL,6,F"The canal is near to their
OL,7,Faccommodation which makes it more
OL,8,Flikely that they will be in that area."
OL,10,FShe concluded: "In my opinion there is
OL,11,Fa risk that future deaths could occur
OL,12,Funless action is taken."
OL,14,FIn a statement, the Canals & River
OL,15,FTrust said: "Our thoughts are with the
OL,16,Ffamily and friends of William Webb
OL,17,Ffollowing his tragic death last
OL,18,FNovember.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@gO]rD@POUtD@XO]wD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
